Win32/mIRC version 0.04
=======================

Win32::mIRC will allow you to communicate with mIRC via DDE.  

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Win32::DDE::Client

This module also requires that you have mIRC installed and running.

